0:{"buildId":"I3GEKSVLVTWqxcEXDRaWq","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":" CE Marking Certification in Dubai"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:30:40+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"CE Marking Certification in Dubai\n\n            Wizms is one of the leading ISO consultants in Dubai. We are having 100% track record of success for CE"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"CE Marking Certification in Dubai"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Wizms is one of the leading ISO consultants in Dubai. We are having 100% track record of success for CE Marking Certification in Dubai. We are one the recognized CE marking consultant in Dubai. Our experts’ team are well knowledge about the industries best practices and can deliver on-time. CE Mark certification cost is always reasonable in Dubai. We are one of the best CE mark consultant in Dubai when compared to other consultants in Dubai."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Steps Involved In CE Mark Certification In Dubai"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 1: Identify EU directives."}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 2: Depending upon the product conformity, different types of conformity assessment modules are prescribed."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 3: Identify applicable regulations"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 4: Identify the applicable standards"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 5: Test the product either manually or in lab."}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 6: Prepare technical related documents."}],["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 7: Write and sign the declaration of conformity."}],["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Step 8: Attest CE mark on the product."}],["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Important section to get CE mark certificate in Dubai:"}],["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Directives: The product must be categorized in terms of EU directives which comes under CE regulations to get CE Marking Certification in Dubai."}],["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Standards: Each identified directive may contain multiple testing, to test the product. List of standards are available in EU directives. Among the available standards, select the standard that suits the product."}],["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Declaration of Conformity: It is a type of document where the manufacturer declares that the product has met the requirements based on the standards and directives. Once the declaration of conformity is signed from the manufacturer, third-party will declare that the product is compliant and provide the compliant certification."}],"$L2","$L3","$L4","$L5","$L6"]}],"$L7"]}]}],["$L8"],"$L9"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
2:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"CE Mark Certification services in Dubai:"}]
3:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"CE mark certification services in Dubai ensures that there is no loophole will be testing the product. CE Mark certification consultant in Dubai is the right choice for the organizations in Dubai, who have vast experience in implementing the CE marking requirements and can help the companies whether the products needs to be certified before taking the product to the European market."}]
4:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"It is easy to get CE Marking Certification in Dubai, if the product is categorized based on the type of product being manufactured. Identify the directives based on the categorized product. Hence testing must be conducted on the categorized product."}]
5:["$","p","18",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Like CE Marking certification, another famous certification in Dubai is ISO 9001 certification. ISO 9001 certification in Dubai is based on Quality Management System (QMS)."}]
6:["$","p","19",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"If you require assistance in CE Marking Certification in Dubai of any products, Wizms is there to help you in all the CE marking certification process. To get more information about the directives that are available in EU regulations, you can reach us through our website or call us at 00971 52 6325363. Wizms offer consulting services in Dubai, Sharjah, Abu Dhabi, Al Ain, Ras al-Khaimah, Fujairah, UAE."}]
